Terre_Haute.Williams-Warren-Zimmerman House: Williams-Warren-Zimmerman House, also known as the Cottage-Among-the-Lindens, is a historic home located at Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana. It was built between 1849 and 1854, and is a 1 1/2-story, Greek Revival style frame dwelling with a one-story wing. It sits on a stucoed brick foundation, is sheathed in clapboard siding, and has a gable roof with dormers.
